<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #10B981; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .footer { background-color: #333; color: white; padding: 20px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px; border-radius: 8px; }
        .success-box { background-color: #D1FAE5; border-left: 4px solid #10B981; padding: 20px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
        .info-box { background-color: #E0F2FE; border-left: 4px solid #3B82F6; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-radius: 4px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background-color: #10B981; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; font-weight: bold; }
        .button:hover { background-color: #059669; }
        .details { background-color: white; padding: 15px; margin: 15px 0; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; }
        .details p { margin: 8px 0; }
        .icon { font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="icon">✓</div>
            <h1 style="margin: 0;">KYC Verification Approved!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{organizationName}},</p>

            <div class="success-box">
                <h2 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #065F46;">Congratulations!</h2>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0; font-size: 16px;">Your KYC (Know Your Customer) verification has been successfully approved. Your organization is now fully verified on CitadelBuy.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="details">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1F2937;">Verification Details</h3>
                <p><strong>Organization:</strong> {{organizationName}}</p>
                <p><strong>Application ID:</strong> {{applicationId}}</p>
                <p><strong>Verification Score:</strong> {{verificationScore}}/100</p>
                <p><strong>Approved Date:</strong> {{approvedDate}}</p>
                {{#if verifiedComponents}}
                <p><strong>Verified Components:</strong></p>
                <ul style="margin: 5px 0;">
                    {{#if idVerified}}<li>Identity Document ✓</li>{{/if}}
                    {{#if addressVerified}}<li>Address Proof ✓</li>{{/if}}
                    {{#if businessVerified}}<li>Business Documents ✓</li>{{/if}}
                </ul>
                {{/if}}
            </div>

            <div class="info-box">
                <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1E40AF;">What's Next?</h3>
                <p style="margin: 5px 0;">With your verified status, you can now:</p>
                <ul style="margin: 10px 0;">
                    <li>Access premium features and higher transaction limits</li>
                    <li>Build trust with customers through your verified badge</li>
                    <li>Participate in exclusive marketplace opportunities</li>
                    <li>Enable advanced payment processing options</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="button">Access Your Dashboard</a>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">Your verification status will remain active as long as your account is in good standing. If you have any questions, our support team is here to help.</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">Thank you for completing the verification process!</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px; color: #6B7280; font-size: 14px;">
                Best regards,<br>
                <strong>The CitadelBuy Team</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>CitadelBuy</strong> - Secure E-Commerce Platform</p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0;">If you have questions, contact us at {{supportEmail}}</p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0;">&copy; {{currentYear}} CitadelBuy. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0; font-size: 11px;">
                This is an automated notification. Please do not reply to this email.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
